    <p><font color="#000000">The computer instantly and accurately scores the charts in between each test, so we will know which questions they did good on and did bad on, before we go on to the next test chart 5 minutes later.</font></p>
    <p><font color="#000000">If all guidelines and instructions are followed, we can expect in the area of 95% accuracy.<br />
